{"tid":1392566,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[再推, 究極和理] 常設仲裁法院","createTime":"2019-07-31T19:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T19:31:59.000Z","uid":295455,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8001f0b3760eb937d425bdf8c0e5c916f21a15a","tid":1392566,"uid":295455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在此小弟跪求文宣及有識之士幫助!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1390835/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1390835/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n註:<br />\n<br />\n海牙 有 國際法庭 同 <strong>常設仲裁法院</strong>. <br />\n<br />\n國際法庭 (ICJ-CIJ): 只有主權國家間的爭端才可以提交國際法院裁决.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>常設仲裁法院 (PCA-CPA):</strong> 與國際法院不同，常設仲裁法院並不是一個國家之間的法庭。爭議雙方可以請求該院對其進行仲裁、調解或者僅僅是調查事實。該院不僅接受來自國家間的申請，同時也接受國家與<strong>私人團體或者個人之間</strong>的衝突解決申請。<br />\n(Source: Wiki)"},{"pid":"85663d540716bb12f35ffd0c75649b06bf9e19e3","tid":1392566,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:31:59.000Z","msg":"義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n邊個最唔想成立獨立調查委員會？777、犬同三毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n危急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}